            <title><![CDATA[[衰]#女生无意将沃柑放柜子1周变霉球# 发霉的水果，没有霉变的部分能吃吗[疑问]？展青霉素是水果中常见的真菌毒素，它会在烂水果的果肉中蔓延，没有长霉的地方也...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A0%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%86%E6%B2%83%E6%9F%91%E6%94%BE%E6%9F%9C%E5%AD%901%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%9C%89%E7%90%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A0%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%86%E6%B2%83%E6%9F%91%E6%94%BE%E6%9F%9C%E5%AD%901%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%9C%89%E7%90%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女生无意将沃柑放柜子1周变霉球#</span></a> 发霉的水果，没有霉变的部分能吃吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>？<br><br>展青霉素是水果中常见的真菌毒素，它会在烂水果的果肉中蔓延，没有长霉的地方也会有看不见的霉菌存在。<br><br>展青霉素会破坏肠道、损伤肾功能，甚至可能致癌！更可怕的是，它的耐热性极强，高温蒸煮也很难破坏或降低它们的毒性。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子提醒：发霉水果，千万别吃！！！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（广东疾控）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk9r65gowfj20wi0npjs7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
